title: #242: A Thousand Whys to Doi (Happy Halloween)
itunes:title: A Thousand Whys to Doi (Happy Halloween)
description: Happy Halloween! To celebrate the holiday, I talked to a bunch of people about the different ways they fear dying. Everybody has their little irrational fears about dying in some normal situation. Here are some of those fears. Short and sweet so you can have more time to trick or treat for razor blades.
